    {
      "text": "A 25-year-old woman is just being shifted to the recovery room after an appendectomy. She feels nauseous. Which of the following is the most appropriate antiemetic for this patient?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Ondansetron"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Aprepitant"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Domperidone"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Hyoscine"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 0,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct answer: A) Ondansetron</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation: </strong></p>\n\n<p>The drug of choice for <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"8f584900e71692777196a6e8943d4e\">postoperative</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"9a8412e39e1692777193c550a5dbb4\">nausea</span> and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"998fb41ebc1692777202e46891c4a7\">vomiting</span> is<strong> ondansetron.</strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Classification of Antiemetics:</strong></p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:703px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Drug class</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Examples</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Uses</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Anticholinergic (M1 receptor)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Hyoscine (scopolamine) </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>DOC: <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"93772348231692777192fbdc055f11\">motion sickness</span> <strong>(Option D ruled out)</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Antihistamine (H1 receptor)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Diphenhydramine</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Promethazine</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Cyclizine</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Meclizine</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Motion sickness</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>5HT3 antagonist</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Ondansetron </p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Palonosetron</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Dalosetron</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Tropisetron</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Granisetron</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>DOC: early onset chemo-induced vomiting</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>DOC:<strong> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"8f584900e71692777196a6e8943d4e\">Postoperative</span> and postradiotherapy-induced <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"998fb41ebc1692777202e46891c4a7\">vomiting</span> (Option A)</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>D2 blocker</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Metoclopramide</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Domperidone </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>Mild to moderate vomiting</li>\n\t\t\t\t<li>GERD <strong>(Option C ruled out)</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>NK1 inhibitor</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Aprepitant</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Fosaprepitant</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Netupitant</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:center\">Rolapitant</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li>DOC: late-onset chemotherapy-induced vomiting <strong>(Option B ruled out)</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>",
