    {
      "text": "A 64-year-old male patient with a history of lung cancer undergoing chemotherapy comes to the clinic with complaints of dizziness and red eyes for 4 days. He complained of chemotherapy-induced nausea and vomiting 5 days ago, for which he was prescribed an antiemetic. Which of the following antiemetics would have led to his current presentation?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 0,
          "text": "Ondansetron"
        },
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Metoclopramide"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Aprepitant"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Dranabinol"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 3,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct answer: D) Dranabinol</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation: </strong></p>\n\n<p>Dronabinol causes <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"9402185d4b1692777189cb62891ff1\">hypotension</span> (leading to dizziness) and bloodshot eyes.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Mechanism of action:</strong> CB1 <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"7d8d28cda71692777180c89a3c86ce\">agonist</span> (Cannabinoid receptor) </p>\n\n<p><strong>Uses: </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Chemotherapy-induced <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"9a8412e39e1692777193c550a5dbb4\">nausea</span> and vomiting</li>\n\t<li>Appetite stimulation.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>ADVERSE EFFECTS OF <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"9aae1ba58a1692777186d3a96d0728\">DRONABINOL</span> : </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>CNS effects :</strong>\n\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Exacerbation of mania, depression, and schizophrenia</li>\n\t\t<li>Dizziness</li>\n\t\t<li>Fatigue</li>\n\t\t<li>Cognitive impairment</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li><strong>Cardiovascular effects :</strong>\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Tachycardia</li>\n\t\t<li>Hypotension or hypertension</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li><strong>Conjunctival congestion</strong></li>\n\t<li>Occasional <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"1665a40f1016927771801899eaed5d\">abdominal</span> pain, nausea, and <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"998fb41ebc1692777202e46891c4a7\">vomiting</span> are potentially indicative of <strong>cannabinoid <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"82dc97494b1692777189e077dc94f9\">hyperemesis</span> syndrome.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:666px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Drug </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Side effect</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ondansetron </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Constipation, QT interval prolongation, headache <strong>(Option A ruled out)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Metoclopramide</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Extrapyramidal side effects (by crossing the blood brain barrier) <strong>(Option B ruled out)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Aprepitant </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\">QT interval prolongation <strong>(Option C ruled out)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>",
